pageContext.claim: “The 'Justice' Department and the FBI have done nothing about the 2020 Presidential Election Voter Fraud, the biggest SCAM in our nation's history, despite overwhelming evidence. They should be ashamed. History will remember. Never give up. See everyone in D.C. on January 6th.”
pageContext.analysis: The Justice Department cannot bring cases if there is no evidence. Trump continues with his hyperbolic claims while touting the Jan. 6 rally in Washington that led to the Capitol riot.
